      "options": {
        "content": "# \ud83e\uddea Pruebas de Rendimiento - TodoMercado API\n\nEste tablero muestra el comportamiento de la API bajo diferentes niveles de carga.\nLos colores indican: \ud83d\udfe2 Saludable | \ud83d\udfe1 Precauci\u00f3n | \ud83d\udd34 Cr\u00edtico\n\n**Test: $test_name**\n\n| Test | Usuarios | Tipo | Descripci\u00f3n |\n|------|----------|------|-------------|\n| 01_smoke | 1 VU | \ud83e\uddea Smoke | Verificar endpoints b\u00e1sicos |\n| 02_load_50 | **50 VUs** | \ud83d\udea6 Load | Carga media sostenida |\n| 03_load_200 | 200 VUs | \ud83d\udcc8 Load | Carga alta sostenida |\n| 04_stress_500 | 500 VUs | \ud83d\udd25 Stress | Punto de quiebre |\n| 05_spike | Spike | \ud83d\udca5 Spike | Picos repentinos |\n| 06_soak_200 | 200 VUs | \ud83d\udca7 Soak | Resistencia prolongada |\n\n**Percentil: $percentile**",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.2.0",
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Disponibilidad",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.2.0",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 90
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 95
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "(1 - sum(increase(k6_http_req_failed_total{test=\"$test_name\", condition=\"nonzero\"}[$__range])) / sum(increase(k6_http_reqs_total{test=\"$test_name\"}[$__range]))) * 100",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "disponibilidad"
        }
      ]
    },
